HUMAN
The most common of the races, humans are hardy and have a tenacity for achievement in their relatively short lives.
ELF
Elves are the most elegant race, favoring magic and nimble stature, often caring for the more delicate things in life.
DWARF
Known for large, mountainous civilizations, Dwarves are master craftsmen and can be ruthless warriors.
DEVIL
Shunned by society as offsprings of black magic, Devilpeople are forever attempting to redeem themselves in the eyes of society... or trying to fight back against it.
